quran[31]{c,v,t,f}:
  77,20,"Kwani hatukukuumbeni kwa maji ya kudharauliwa? <sup>20</sup>","[20] Kwani hatukukuumbeni kutokana na maji yaliyo dhalili, nayo ni manii,"
  77,21,"Kisha tukayaweka mahali pa utulivu madhubuti? <sup>21</sup>","[21] Na tukayaweka maji haya katika pahala patulivu,"
  77,22,"Mpaka muda maalumu? <sup>22</sup>","[22] Mpaka kutimilia kuumbwa kwake na kutengenezwa kwake kwa muda anao ujua Mwenyezi Mungu."
  77,23,"Tukakadiria na Sisi ni wabora wa kukadiria. <sup>23</sup>","[23] Nasi tukaweka vipimo katika kuumbwa kwake, na kutengenezwa kwake, na kutoka kwake. Basi wabora wa kupima na kukadiria ni Sisi."
  77,24,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>24</sup>","[24] Ole wao hao wanao kadhibisha neema za kuumba na kukadiria."
  77,25,"Kwani hatukuifanya ardhi yenye kukusanya <sup>25</sup>","[25] Kwani hatukuifanya ardhi kuwa imekusanya juu ya mgongo wake"
  77,26,"Walio hai na maiti? <sup>26</sup>","[26] Viumbe vilivyo hai visio hisabika, na vilio kufa visio kadirika,"
  77,27,"Na ndani yake tukaweka milima mirefu yenye kuthibiti, na tunakunywesheni maji matamu? <sup>27</sup>","[27] Na tukaweka milima iliyo thibiti imara mirefu, na tukakunywesheni maji matamu?"
  77,28,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>28</sup>","[28] Wataangamia siku hiyo hao wanao kadhibisha neema hizi!"
  77,29,"Nendeni kwenye adhabu mliyo kuwa mkiikanusha! <sup>29</sup>","[29] Siku ya kupambanua wataambiwa makafiri: Nendeni huko Motoni mliko kuwa mkikukanusha."
  77,30,"Nendeni kwenye kivuli chenye mapande matatu! <sup>30</sup>","[30] Nendeni kwenye joto la moshi wa Jahannamu ulio gawika kwa ukubwa wake mapande matatu."
  77,31,"Hakikingi moto, wala hakiwaepushi na mwako. <sup>31</sup>","[31] Hapana cha kujikinga na joto la siku hiyo, wala kivuli hicho hakipunguzi joto la mwako hata kidogo."
  77,32,"Hakika Moto huo unatoa macheche kama majumba! <sup>32</sup>","[32] Moto huo hutupa macheche yenye ukubwa kama majumba,"
  77,33,"Kama kwamba ni ngamia wa rangi ya manjano! <sup>33</sup>","[33] Au utaona hayo macheche kama ngamia weusi wenye kuingia rangi ya manjano."
  77,34,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>34</sup>","[34] Wataangamia siku hiyo wanao kanusha kwamba hizi ndizo sifa za Moto."
  77,35,"Hii ni siku ambayo hawatatamka kitu, <sup>35</sup>","[35] Haya uliyo simuliwa yatatokea katika siku ambayo hawatatamka kitu cha kuwanufaisha,"
  77,36,"Wala hawataruhusiwa kutoa udhuru. <sup>36</sup>","[36] Wala hawatakuwa na idhini ya kutamka, wala hawatatoa udhuru, kwani hawana udhuru."
  77,37,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao walio kanusha! <sup>37</sup>","[37] Wataangamia siku hiyo wanayo ikadhibisha siku hii."
  77,38,"Hii ndiyo siku ya kupambanua. Tumekukusanyeni nyinyi na walio tangulia. <sup>38</sup>","[38] Hii ndiyo siku ya kufafanua baina ya mwenye ukweli, na mwenye uwongo, kwa kuwa kila mmoja atalipwa kwa mujibu wa anavyo stahiki. Enyi mnao mkadhibisha Muhammad! Tumekujaalieni nyinyi na walio kutangulieni walio kadhibisha mfano wenu,"
  77,39,"kiwa mnayo hila, nifanyieni hila Mimi! <sup>39</sup>","[39] Kama mnayo hila ya kujikinga na adhabu basi fanyeni hila hiyo. Basi njooni muepukane na adhabu yangu."
  77,40,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao walio kanusha! <sup>40</sup>","[40] Wataangamia siku hiyo wanayo ikadhibisha ahadi ya Mwenyezi Mungu."
  77,41,"Hakika wachamngu watakuwa katika vivuli na chemchem, <sup>41</sup>","[41] Hakika wachamngu wenye kujikinga na adhabu ya Mwenyezi Mungu watakuwa katika kivuli kikubwa, na chemchem zinazo miminika,"
  77,42,"Na matunda wanayo yapenda, <sup>42</sup>","[42] Na matunda wanayo yaonea ladha, na wanayo yapenda,"
  77,43,"Kuleni na kunyweni kwa furaha kwa yale mliyo kuwa mkiyatenda. <sup>43</sup>","[43] Wataambiwa kwa kuamkiwa na kukirimiwa: Kuleni na mnywe chakula na vinywaji kwa starehe kwa sababu ya vitendo vyema mlivyo kuwa mkivitenda duniani."
  77,44,"Hakika ndio kama hivyo tunavyo walipa watendao mema. <sup>44</sup>","[44] Hakika Sisi huwalipa mfano wa malipo hayo matukufu watu wema."
  77,45,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>45</sup>","[45] Wataangamia siku hiyo wanayo ikadhibisha Pepo."
  77,46,"Kuleni na mjifurahishe kidogo tu. Hakika nyinyi ni wakosefu! <sup>46</sup>","[46] Na makafiri wataambiwa: Kuleni na mjistareheshe kwa starehe isiyo baki muda mrefu, kwani hakika nyinyi ni wakosefu kwa kumshirikisha kwenu Mwenyezi Mungu."
  77,47,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>47</sup>","[47] Wataangamia siku hiyo wanao ikadhibisha neema."
  77,48,"Na wakiambiwa: Inameni! Hawainami. <sup>48</sup>","[48] Na wakiambiwa: Swalini kwa ajili ya Mwenyezi Mungu, na mnyenyekeeni Yeye, hawanyenyekei wala hawaswali; bali hushikilia kiburi chao!"
  77,49,"Ole wao siku hiyo hao wanao kanusha! <sup>49</sup>","[49] Wataangamia siku wanao kadhibisha amri za Mwenyezi Mungu na makatazo yake."
  77,50,"Basi maneno gani baada ya haya watayaamini? <sup>50</sup>","[50] Basi maneno gani hawa watayaamini ikiwa hawaiamini Qur'ani, na hali hii ni muujiza ulio toka mbinguni?"
